<BaseLayout title="Security and Responsible Disclosure | CourtScope"><section class="hero"><div class="prose-width"><p class="eyebrow">Public policy</p><h1>Security and Responsible Disclosure</h1><p class="lede">Please report security issues privately.</p></div></section><section class="section"><div class="prose-width"><div class="card"><p>Do not publish credentials, private records, or exploit details. Email info@courtscope.org with “Security” in the subject. CourtScope uses least privilege, server-side admin authentication, secret scanning, restricted raw evidence, and audit receipts.</p><h2>What controls</h2><p>Official source terms, applicable law, dataset-specific notices, and the current published CourtScope methodology control where they are more specific. Contact <a href="mailto:info@courtscope.org">info@courtscope.org</a> for questions.</p><p><strong>Last updated:</strong> July 11, 2026</p></div></div></section></BaseLayout>